# Force LF line endings for all shell scripts. Vercel runs these via bash
# on Linux and CRLF causes silent "$'\r': command not found" failures
# (the kind that take an hour to diagnose). The Cowork mount sometimes
# converts shell scripts to CRLF when they get re-touched, so we lock it.
*.sh text eol=lf

# Same for any other Linux-executed file
Dockerfile text eol=lf
*.dockerfile text eol=lf
*.bash text eol=lf
